as a designer and
another discipline?

00:10:59.860 --> 00:11:01.402
I know that we're
all kind of cross--

00:11:01.402 --> 00:11:03.276
There's a lot of
disciplines represented here

00:11:03.276 --> 00:11:04.120
in our backgrounds.

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:05.870
We're all doing design-y
stuff now, right?

00:11:05.870 --> 00:11:12.020
So How do you approach that
kind of work flow collaboration

00:11:12.020 --> 00:11:15.710
between someone who might
not understand your skill

00:11:15.710 --> 00:11:17.952
set, and you might
not understand theirs?

