ALEX COOK: I think it's a
combination of conversation

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:21.760
and mutual respect.

00:11:21.760 --> 00:11:25.040
So the end of the day, everybody
wants to do the same thing.

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:26.690
We want to ship
something really great.

